Lifestyle blogger Amanda Chisom has said she doesn’t mind becoming the third wife of popular actor Yul Edochie. With many reacting differently to the news of Yul Edochie’s second wife and infant son, the communication consultant via her Facebook page has now signified interest in assuming the actor’s third wife if need be. Amanda Chisom commended Yul’s action as she noted embracing polygamy means going back to the original African roots. The social media personality complimented the movie star’s little son.   ‘Most ladies condemning polygamy date married…     I’ve never seen a faithful actor, says Iyabo Ojo     Meet Yul Edochie’s second wife   She also noted with Yul’s kind of voice that’s captivates her soul, she doesn’t mind being a third wife if they would produce such cute son like little Star Dike Munachimso Yul-Edochie. Sharing photos of Yul with his new wife and son, Chisom wrote: “Wonders shall not cease, so Yul with all the lovey Dovey has a second wife, and a son and he is so cute. “We are going back to our root. Polygamy wey no dey stressful. I like this. Gistlover dey plan disgrace, guy man use him hand bring the story. He has a second wife, his wife is aware, gini emezia. “I don’t know if he needs a third wife because his voice na agbakam isi and if the son will look this fine, I am in.”